        <abstract> 
<p>Rejoices over news of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> sales.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Pall Mall Gazette</hi> review [7 (1868): 555, 636, 652] is undoubtedly by G. H. Lewes [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">5951</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Dinner at Lyells’.</p>
            <p>Dean Stanley favours a monument to Faraday in Westminster Abbey.</p>
            <p>Perceval Wright is back from Seychelles and reports on plants he collected.</p>
